{"tid":1308154,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【不見不散，不撤不散】我想將呢首歌送俾幾位義士","createTime":"2019-07-11T22:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T22:45:25.000Z","uid":273803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0abccd7302692617dfcdcbf1831e6d91b60b535a","tid":1308154,"uid":273803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:42:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sepYcxaMzEg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsepYcxaMzEg&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0PzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=e79aceb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sepYcxaMzEg</a><br />\n<br />\n一直都好喜歡Beyond三子時期嘅《不見不散》<br />\n首歌講到理想好遙遠，但係為咗對逝者嘅承諾，再絕望都一定會堅持落去<br />\n<br />\n啱啱聽嘅時候諗起幾位義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發現歌詞入面嘅「不見不散」其實可以換成「不撤不散」<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n-<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n不撤不散<br />\n不撤不散<br />\n我會等你<br />\n與你走進這空間<br />\n<br />\n不撤不散<br />\n不撤不散<br />\n我會等你<br />\n與你跨過這高山<br />\n<br />\n理想<br />\n或遠在無邊的遠方<br />\n還是已淡忘<br />\n<br />\n承諾<br />\n讓我在無止地期待<br />\n我只有活<br />\n<br />\n在活在未來<br />\n我已等到枯乾<br />\n但未感到絕望<br />\n完全是因你<br />\n可以在旁<br />\n<br />\n我會奏著哀歌<br />\n替你點亮燭光<br />\n<br />\n你縱使一去<br />\n不再復返<br />\n不撤不散<br />\n不撤不散<br />\n不撤不散<br />\n我會相信<br />\n<br />\n縱是風里飛花<br />\n不撤不散<br />\n不撤不散 <br />\n我會相信<br />\n教我相信好嗎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2dba8f0fe51264c8a446ace4f350e3f8319eea","tid":1308154,"uid":273803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XCA8xay.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXCA8xay.jpg&h=655d17e0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}